THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS

This repository bundles third-party HDL, each retaining its own copyright and
licence notice in its source file headers. Those notices must be preserved.

  src/fpga/rtl/T80/          Z80 CPU core. BSD-style licence (see file headers).
                             Copyright (c) 2001-2002 Daniel Wallner
                               <jesus@opencores.org> -- original author
                             Copyright (c) 2018 Sorgelig -- v350 "T80(c)"
                             With further work by MikeJ (v300, fpgaarcade.com),
                             Sean Riddle (v301) and TobiFlex (v303).

  src/fpga/core/mem/         SDRAM controller. MIT licence (see file headers).
  src/fpga/core/             data_loader, sound_i2s, sync_fifo. MIT.
                             Copyright (c) 2022-2023 Adam Gastineau (agg23)

  src/fpga/apf/              Analogue Pocket openFPGA framework (APF).
                             Copyright (c) Analogue Enterprises Limited.
                             Used under the Analogue Pocket EULA:
                             https://www.analogue.link/pocket-eula

The hardware behaviour implemented here was derived from MAME's `kingobox`
driver by Ernesto Corvi (dataeast/kingobox.cpp, BSD-3-Clause). No MAME source
code is included in this repository.

No arcade ROM data is included in this repository. ROM images are built by the
user from romsets they already own.
